That's it.

14:40.588 --> 14:42.089
That's what?

14:42.131 --> 14:43.800
I can't take this anymore.

14:43.842 --> 14:46.302
You are the most selfish,

14:43.842 --> 14:46.302
thoughtless person

14:46.344 --> 14:47.721
