You're breaking up with me?

14:51.349 --> 14:52.933
You have  killed

14:52.975 --> 14:55.353
everything I have

14:52.975 --> 14:55.353
ever felt for you.

14:52.975 --> 14:55.353
It's over!

14:55.395 --> 14:57.564
But, but what am I going to do?

14:57.605 --> 14:59.190
I never want to

14:57.605 --> 14:59.190
